subtitleNullable: Building Sales in Connecticut with Georeferencing
descriptionNullable:
This dataset comprises a collection of parameters used for sales analysis in the state of Connecticut. These databases are sourced from a repository on GitHub and the respective official sources of the state of Connecticut:

Github (Spanish): https://github.com/ksmorgadog/salesdatabi

# Data Description:

* CT_Municipalities.csv: It contains the main data of the state of Connecticut, divided by city and county.
* FipCodes.xlsx: Excel File with the data used for localization
* Real_Estate_Sales_2001-2020_GL.csv: Main prices file, where it is presented the data of sales for each building by year
